{"about_the_game":"Z Arena is an FPS survival game where you stand as the last line of defense against relentless waves of zombies. Featuring classic wave-based gameplay across various maps, you\u2019ll face ever-increasing challenges while striving to survive.<br><br>There are no limits\u2014you can keep slaying zombies as long as you want. Level up to unlock more powerful weapons and upgrade them to take down enemies faster. The game also offers a &quot;Missions&quot; mode, with focused challenges that test your skills in different scenarios.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">MISSIONS MODE</h2></strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411460/extras/ezgif.com-gif-maker__3_.gif?t=1731936511\" /><br><br>The Missions mode puts you in various scenarios where your objective is to survive and complete specific tasks. Progress through different environments and face different challenges as you take on hordes of zombies.<br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">ENDLESS WAVES</h2></strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411460/extras/zgifkill-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731936511\" /><br><br>Endless mode is a classic wave after wave of zombies. Collect achievements across different maps, experiment with new and upgraded weapons, and see how long you can last.<br><br><strong>GAMEPLAY</strong><br><br>The Missions mode offers a variety of objectives across diverse environments, each with unique challenges that require both strategy and quick reflexes. Whether you\u2019re battling through tight spaces or wide-open areas overrun by zombies, every level is designed to test your survival skills. Endless mode provides limitless replayability with new achievements, levels, and powerful weapon upgrades, allowing you to eliminate hordes with style. Smooth gameplay and responsive camera controls deliver an immersive experience.<br><br><strong>UPGRADING WEAPONS</strong><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1411460/extras/zgif-ezgif.com-video-to-gif-converter.gif?t=1731936511\" /><br><br>Standard weapons in endless mode are fully upgradable, offering improvements such as better accuracy, increased ammo capacity, scopes, and more. Upgrade stations are strategically placed on each map in endless mode, ensuring that you always have the chance to enhance your arsenal.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Missions mode with challenging objectives across various environments.<br></li><li> Endless mode with upgradable weapons and multiple maps to explore.<br></li><li> Over 15 unique enemy types with increasingly challenging behavior.<br></li><li> Timed kill streak.<br></li><li> Special super weapons.<br></li><li> Original Soundtracks.<br></li><li> Steam Achievements.</li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Beginning of The End","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/bba19aee1a2b0e3b06f8c2ee2d406f36f830c33a.jpg"},{"name":"Explorer","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/760897e615b1cd65e7c1d43be3e66bc92d317870.jpg"},{"name":"Better Come Faster","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/d5d8d0fbb26400b509279d2a9966586f0f987b23.jpg"},{"name":"Waiting For More!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/fc133901b1abc894665d21d164b372b7aab8b0e9.jpg"},{"name":"No One Can Stop Me!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/3e7a9e85bd7bdd0c528868fb451de25765850815.jpg"},{"name":"Weapons Master","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1411460/efec2a428eee5c66cfd5568b57b10a5a4689235b.jpg"},{"name":"Special Machine","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/pub